subject: Baseball
Squirrels
Citizens Bank Park (Philadelphia, Pa)
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: The Cardinals have rallied around the Rally Squirrel after it darted across home plate in Game 4 and St. Louis came back to beat the Phillies.
